# PROMPT TEMPLATE: Creazione Pagina Articolo Research

Crea una pagina HTML completa per un articolo scientifico/medico seguendo ESATTAMENTE questa struttura e design. Non aggiungere, rimuovere o modificare il contenuto dell'articolo fornito - utilizzalo così com'è.

## SPECIFICHE TECNICHE HTML:

### HEAD SECTION:
- DOCTYPE html5, lang="it"
- Meta viewport responsive
- Title: "[TITOLO ARTICOLO] | Dr. Benjamin De Ornelas"
- Meta description con sommario dell'articolo (max 160 caratteri)
- Meta keywords pertinenti al contenuto
- Canonical URL
- Open Graph meta tags (title, description, type="article", url)
- Favicon: `/assets/img/favicon.svg`
- Tailwind CSS: `https://cdn.tailwindcss.com`
- Google Fonts: Inter (400,500,600,700,800) + JetBrains Mono (400,500)
- Lucide Icons: `https://unpkg.com/lucide@latest`
- AOS animations: `https://unpkg.com/aos@2.3.1/dist/aos.css` e JS

### CSS PERSONALIZZATO (includi sempre):
```css
html { scroll-behavior: smooth; }
body {
  font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
  -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;
  -moz-osx-font-smoothing: grayscale;
}
.gradient-text {
  background: linear-gradient(90deg, #38bdf8, #a78bfa);
  -webkit-background-clip: text;
  -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
  background-clip: text;
  color: transparent;
}
.glass-card {
  background: rgba(30, 41, 59, 0.5);
  backdrop-filter: blur(12px);
  -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(12px);
  border: 1px solid rgba(51, 65, 85, 0.5);
  transition: all 0.3s ease;
}
.research-table {
  overflow-x: auto;
}
.research-table table {
  min-width: 100%;
  border-collapse: collapse;
}
.research-table th,
.research-table td {
  padding: 12px 16px;
  text-align: left;
  border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(51, 65, 85, 0.5);
}
.research-table th {
  background: rgba(56, 189, 248, 0.1);
  font-weight: 600;
  color: #38bdf8;
}
.algorithm-step {
  background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(56, 189, 248, 0.1), rgba(167, 139, 250, 0.1));
  border-left: 4px solid #38bdf8;
  margin-bottom: 1rem;
}
.citation {
  color: #94a3b8;
  font-size: 0.9em;
  font-style: italic;
}
.highlight-box {
  background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(56, 189, 248, 0.05), rgba(167, 139, 250, 0.05));
  border: 1px solid rgba(56, 189, 248, 0.2);
}
```

## STRUTTURA HTML BODY:

### 1. BACKGROUND DECORATIVO:
```html
<body class="bg-slate-900 text-gray-200">
  <div class="absolute top-0 left-0 right-0 -z-10 h-screen w-full">
    <div class="absolute inset-0 -z-10 h-full w-full bg-slate-900 bg-[linear-gradient(to_right,#1e293b_1px,transparent_1px),linear-gradient(to_bottom,#1e293b_1px,transparent_1px)] bg-[size:4rem_4rem]"></div>
    <div class="absolute top-0 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 -z-10 h-96 w-full max-w-4xl rounded-full bg-sky-500/20 blur-3xl"></div>
  </div>
```

### 2. CONTAINER PRINCIPALE:
```html
<div class="container mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 max-w-4xl">
```

### 3. HEADER STICKY:
```html
<header class="sticky top-0 z-50 py-4 transition-all duration-300">
  <div class="glass-card rounded-xl px-4 py-2">
    <nav class="flex items-center justify-between">
      <a href="/" class="text-xl font-bold tracking-tighter text-white flex items-center gap-2">
        <i data-lucide="heart-pulse" class="text-sky-400"></i>
        Dr. Benjamin De Ornelas
      </a>
      <ul class="hidden md:flex items-center space-x-1">
        <li><a href="/" class="px-3 py-2 rounded-md hover:bg-slate-700/50">Home</a></li>
        <li><a href="/about/" class="px-3 py-2 rounded-md hover:bg-slate-700/50">Chi Sono</a></li>
        <li><a href="/research/" class="px-3 py-2 rounded-md bg-sky-500/20 text-sky-400">Ricerca</a></li>
        <li><a href="/contact/" class="ml-4 bg-sky-500 hover:bg-sky-600 text-white font-medium py-2 px-4 rounded-lg">Contatti</a></li>
      </ul>
    </nav>
  </div>
</header>
```

### 4. BREADCRUMB:
```html
<nav class="text-sm text-slate-400 mb-8" data-aos="fade-up">
  <a href="/" class="hover:text-sky-400">Home</a> 
  <span class="mx-2">/</span> 
  <a href="/research/" class="hover:text-sky-400">Ricerca</a>
  <span class="mx-2">/</span>
  <span class="text-white">[TITOLO BREVE]</span>
</nav>
```

### 5. HEADER ARTICOLO:
```html
<header class="mb-12" data-aos="fade-up">
  <div class="glass-card rounded-xl p-8 md:p-12">
    <div class="flex items-center gap-2 text-sky-400 text-sm font-medium mb-4">
      <i data-lucide="microscope" class="w-4 h-4"></i>
      [CATEGORIA] • [SOTTO-CATEGORIA]
    </div>
    <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold tracking-tight mb-6">
      <span class="gradient-text">[PRIMA PARTE TITOLO]</span><br>
      <span class="text-white">[SECONDA PARTE TITOLO]</span>
    </h1>
    <p class="text-xl text-slate-300 leading-relaxed mb-8">
      [SOTTOTITOLO SE PRESENTE]
    </p>
    <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-4 text-sm text-slate-400">
      <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
        <i data-lucide="calendar" class="w-4 h-4"></i>
        [DATA]
      </div>
      <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
        <i data-lucide="clock" class="w-4 h-4"></i>
        [TEMPO LETTURA] min di lettura
      </div>
      <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
        <i data-lucide="tag" class="w-4 h-4"></i>
        [TAGS SEPARATI DA VIRGOLA]
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</header>
```

### 6. ARTICOLO PRINCIPALE:
```html
<article class="glass-card rounded-xl p-8 md:p-12 mb-12" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="200">
  <!-- QUI INSERISCI IL CONTENUTO DELL'ARTICOLO SEGUENDO QUESTE REGOLE: -->
```

## REGOLE PER LA FORMATTAZIONE DEL CONTENUTO:

### A. SEZIONI PRINCIPALI:
```html
<section class="mb-12">
  <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-6 flex items-center gap-2">
    <i data-lucide="[ICONA]" class="w-6 h-6 text-[COLORE]-400"></i>
    [TITOLO SEZIONE]
  </h2>
  <!-- contenuto sezione -->
</section>
```

### B. PARAGRAFI:
```html
<p class="text-slate-300 leading-relaxed mb-6">
  [TESTO PARAGRAFO]
</p>
```

### C. LISTE CON STEPS/ALGORITMI:
```html
<div class="algorithm-step rounded-lg p-6">
  <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-3">
    <div class="flex items-center justify-center w-8 h-8 bg-sky-500 text-white rounded-full text-sm font-bold">[NUMERO]</div>
    <h3 class="font-bold text-white">[TITOLO STEP]</h3>
  </div>
  <p class="text-slate-300 ml-11">[DESCRIZIONE STEP]</p>
</div>
```

### D. BOX EVIDENZIATI:
```html
<div class="highlight-box rounded-lg p-6 mb-6">
  <p class="text-slate-300 leading-relaxed">
    <strong class="text-sky-400">[LABEL]</strong>: [CONTENUTO]
  </p>
</div>
```

### E. CITAZIONI:
```html
<div class="border-l-4 border-emerald-400 pl-6">
  <p class="text-slate-300 leading-relaxed">
    [TESTO] <span class="citation">([Autori et al., Anno])</span>
  </p>
</div>
```

### F. TABELLE:
```html
<div class="research-table mb-8">
  <table class="w-full glass-card rounded-lg">
    <thead>
      <tr>
        <th>[HEADER 1]</th>
        <th>[HEADER 2]</th>
      </tr>
    </thead>
    <tbody>
      <tr>
        <td class="font-medium text-white">[CELLA 1]</td>
        <td>[CELLA 2]</td>
      </tr>
    </tbody>
  </table>
</div>
```

### G. BIBLIOGRAFIA:
```html
<section>
  <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-6 flex items-center gap-2">
    <i data-lucide="library" class="w-6 h-6 text-slate-400"></i>
    Bibliografia [O TITOLO ORIGINALE]
  </h2>
  <div class="space-y-3 text-sm">
    <div class="border-l-2 border-slate-600 pl-4">
      <p class="text-slate-300">[CITAZIONE]</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
```

### 7. FOOTER:
```html
<footer class="py-8 border-t border-slate-700/50">
  <div class="text-center">
    <p class="text-slate-400 text-sm mb-4">
      © 2025 Dr. Benjamin De Ornelas. Contenuti a scopo informativo ed educativo.
    </p>
    <div class="flex justify-center gap-6 text-sm">
      <a href="/privacy/" class="text-slate-400 hover:text-sky-400">Privacy Policy</a>
      <a href="/terms/" class="text-slate-400 hover:text-sky-400">Termini d'Uso</a>
      <a href="/contact/" class="text-slate-400 hover:text-sky-400">Contatti</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</footer>
```

### 8. JAVASCRIPT FINALE:
```html
<script>
document.addEventListener('DOMContentLoaded', () => {
  if (window.lucide) lucide.createIcons();
  if (window.AOS) {
    AOS.init({
      duration: 700,
      once: true,
      offset: 50
    });
  }
});
</script>
```

## ISTRUZIONI SPECIFICHE:

1. **NON MODIFICARE IL CONTENUTO**: Usa il testo dell'articolo esattamente come fornito
2. **NON AGGIUNGERE SEZIONI**: Non creare abstract, articoli correlati, o altri contenuti
3. **MANTIENI LA STRUTTURA**: Rispetta l'ordine originale delle sezioni
4. **USA I COLORI**: Alterna colori per le icone (sky-400, violet-400, emerald-400, orange-400, purple-400)
5. **APPLICA AOS**: Aggiungi `data-aos="fade-up"` e delay incrementali
6. **FORMATTA CITAZIONI**: Usa `.citation` class per i riferimenti bibliografici
7. **EVIDENZIA TERMINI**: Usa `<strong class="text-white">` per termini importanti

## ESEMPIO DI USO:

"Crea una pagina HTML per questo articolo seguendo il template fornito: [INSERISCI QUI IL TESTO DELL'ARTICOLO]"
